{"tid":1785400,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"社福罷．一起罷","createTime":"2019-12-16T10:42:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-17T03:35:59.000Z","uid":267569,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6b275d8335348c947a02a41bab21a3f6a125f1dd","tid":1785400,"uid":267569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T10:42:18.000Z","msg":"12月17日便是社福界罷工第一天，很多人問究竟會有多少人罷工？我們不知道，因為社福界罷工從來不易，但不易不代表不為。我們相信不少人已覺醒，大家已明白對抗極權是長期抗爭，連結不同行業，團結香港人，集結隨時啟動三罷的巨大力量，那才是極權最害怕的事情。為了孩子和香港的未來，我們要開始透過工會和不同現有平台集結力量。<br />\n<br />\n罷工是需要鍛煉和習慣，請各社福界同工，各位香港人，明早10am中環愛丁堡廣場見。<br />\n<br />\n現場設哀悼區讓香港人將寫上「失去」的Memo布放下，再從海量黃海中帶走的代表「堅持」和「守護」的「黃頭盔」。<br />\n<br />\n協助摺「黃頭盔」的社福界同工和香港人可將「黃<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wPvGpvp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwPvGpvp.jpg&h=3e321c03&s={SIZE}\" />頭盔」帶到愛丁堡廣場的哀悼區，讓「黃頭盔海」展現香港。<br />\n<br />\n社福界罷工委員會<br />\n<br />\n#五大訴求缺一不可<br />\n#行業罷工促使三罷<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100421891400579/posts/141096267333141?d=n&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100421891400579%2Fposts%2F141096267333141%3Fd%3Dn%26sfns%3Dmo&d=dVEf9brN%2BTtwApumOSMW7oICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=b11f5983\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100421891400579/posts/141096267333141?d=n&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"ef3f8b3bdb7f60ac292c83de6a4fe70d1bdabbcb","tid":1785400,"uid":213784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T11:25:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">請各位喺出post前貼多張日程表or文宣</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">咁文宣組就冇咁忙啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sdw2RCH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsdw2RCH.jpg&h=8da8b8c7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ja88Na2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%